Module 104
📘 Legal Calculus 4.5
Tier 8 — Epilogue & Advanced Testimony
Module 104 – Memory Diplomacy: Engaging Institutions Without War 🕊️🏛️
⚖️ Core Message
Invite collaboration before escalation: share the archive, state the ask, and offer joint verification steps.

📖 Lesson Content
• Tone — Respectful, narrow, verifiable.
• Packet — One‑pager, Top‑5 exhibits, Verification Plan.
• Meeting — 15‑minute call agenda; document outcomes.
• Follow‑up — Written summary and next date.
• Escalation — Oversight only after a clear non‑response.
📝 Assignment
Draft a 1‑page 'Memory Diplomacy' letter to a clerk/judge/admin body with a verification plan and narrow ask.

✅ Model Answer (Template)
LETTER (EXCERPT)
We propose joint verification of Exhibits A–C and a short deficiency guidance within 3 days.

💡 Reflection
Many will help when you make helping easy—and on the record.

🎨 Visual Pairing
Handshake icon over a small hash table labeled A–C.



